Privacy Policy for RAYLL STUDIOS PRIVATE LIMITED
Effective Date:
August 8, 2024
RAYLL STUDIOS PRIVATE LIMITED ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you play our single-player games or interact with our services.
1. Information We Collect
RAYLL STUDIOS PRIVATE LIMITED collects limited personal data typical to single-player games, including but not limited to:
Device Information
: We may collect information about the device you use to play our games, such as hardware model, operating system, and IP address.
Game Analytics
: We collect gameplay data to improve our services, such as level progression, achievements, and game settings.
Crash Reports
: If our games encounter errors, crash reports are generated to help us diagnose and resolve technical issues.
We do not collect personal information such as names, email addresses, or payment details, as our games do not involve such features.
2. Purpose of Data Collection
We collect this data to:
Improve the performance and user experience of our games.
Diagnose and resolve technical issues.
Analyze gameplay trends to optimize our game development.
3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal data to third parties. We may share non-personally identifiable information with our service providers or partners who help us analyze game performance and fix technical issues.
4. User Rights
Since we collect only non-personally identifiable data, we do not offer mechanisms to access, update, or delete personal data. However, users can request that their game data (such as saved games) be deleted by uninstalling the game or contacting us.
5. Data Retention
We retain gameplay data and crash reports for as long as is necessary to achieve the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. Once the data is no longer needed, it will be securely deleted or anonymized.
6. Security Measures
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. These include encryption and secure server infrastructure.
7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
Our games are not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that a child under 13 has provided us with personal data, we will delete such information promptly.
8. International Data Transfers
If you are located outside of India, please note that we may transfer data to India for processing. We comply with applicable data protection laws during such transfers.
9. Updates to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make significant changes, we will notify users via an in-game notice or update our website. Continued use of our services after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
10. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:
RAYLL STUDIOS PRIVATE LIMITED
417, Vasant Enclave, Vasant Vihar-1, New Delhi INDIA - 110057
Email:
